---

<section>
  <img src="/prevtalks.png" alt="" />
  <article>
    <div class="speakerinfo">
      <h3 class="h3thin">Speaker 2024 thin</h3>
      <h2>Navn bold</h2>
      <h3 class="h3bold">stilling bold</h3>
